# Splits
#####################

# split orientation
super + q
  i3-msg split toggle 


#####################
# Layout
#####################

# toggle fullscreen mode for the focused container
super + m
  i3-msg fullscreen toggle

# change container layout
super + {w,e}
  i3-msg layout {tabbed,toggle split}


